### ============================================
### Inventory Service 테스트 (8082)
### 테스트 데이터 준비용
### ============================================

### 1. 상품 등록 (테스트용)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/products?productCode=PROD-001&name=테스트상품&price=10000&initialQuantity=100
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 상품 등록 (두번째 상품)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/products?productCode=PROD-002&name=프리미엄상품&price=50000&initialQuantity=20
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 상품 조회
GET http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/products/1

### 4. 재고 조회
GET http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/1

### 5. 재고 추가 (입고)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/1/add?quantity=50

### 6. 재고 예약 (수동 테스트)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/1/reserve?quantity=5

### 7. 예약 확정 (수동 테스트)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/1/confirm?quantity=5

### 8. 예약 취소 (수동 테스트)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/inventory/1/cancel?quantity=5
